---

<BaseLayout
  title="HubSpot Implementation for Japan GTM: What to Configure First | Consilegy"
  description="An IT back-office SaaS company (approx. 200 employees) configured HubSpot without Japan-specific lifecycle stage definitions, qualification criteria, or Japan market properties. After rebuilding the architecture in the correct order, MQL-to-SQL conversion increased by up to 20%."
