        <h2>HubSpot configured but pipeline data unreliable for Japan?</h2>
        <p>Share how your HubSpot is currently set up for Japan. We'll identify which configuration layers are missing or in the wrong order and what to fix first.</p>
        <div class="article-cta__actions">
          <a href="/en/contact/" class="article-cta__btn article-cta__btn--primary">Contact Us</a>
